text: Ozone is a locale in Bonneville County, Idaho, United States.https://idaho.hometownlocator.com/maps/feature- map,ftc,2,fid,374294,n,ozone.cfm It is located on Bone Road in eastern Idaho. In 1946, 26 people were registered to vote in the Ozone precinct. ==References== Category:Former populated places in Idaho Category:Ghost towns in Idaho
title: Ozone, Idaho
